  "body": "# Feature Issue\r\n\r\nRefactor the `selector` component to use Figma 1-1.\r\n\r\n<img width=\"613\" src=\"https://github.com/status-im/status-mobile/assets/19339952/e22dc1d0-a7e3-4176-9a7c-87338ff2f87d\">\r\n\r\n### Description\r\n\r\nThe selector component has four types (`toggle`, `radio`, `checkbox`,  and `filled-checkbox`), but it's implemented into its own component and makes it difficult to use different types on list components such as the `category` component.\r\n\r\nIt needs to be refactored into a single component matching Figma 1-1 props.\r\n\r\n### Acceptance Criteria\r\n\r\nThe usage of this component should be updated across the codebase\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n",
